post.title: Volunteers Needed for the Cleveland Airshow

post.content: We need more help at the Cleveland Airshow! We must fill 50 more spots on Sunday, August 31st, and 66 more spots on Monday, September 1st.& This is one of our largest fundraisers and we need to fill these spots to make the $10,000 this year and to keep the fundraiser for next year. Please make time in your schedule to fill these spots. Volunteers must be at least 15 years old or be an incoming freshman. Volunteers may be other family members or friends! Below is more information regarding this event. If you can help, please contact Kathy Pishnery at 440-503-5457 or kathypish@aol.com.
